The paper focuses on developing an autonomous system for drones to race using onboard resources, which involves visual navigation and control strategies. Therefore, the most likely category is Robotics (cs.RO), followed by Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves control strategies, which could fall under Systems and Control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which could fall under Machine Learning (cs.LG).
